{"tid":970004,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【低手改詞】有一種悲傷 - 粵語版本","createTime":"2019-01-05T13:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T14:42:42.000Z","uid":37464,"like":19,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"deb228d7e202ce778f81d7e31883c9d55e349c47","tid":970004,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/gGXs-BBLwFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgGXs-BBLwFU&d=jMjk5J0i9ROHC9B6UTxRvl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=065e01c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/gGXs-BBLwFU</a><br />\n作曲：張簡君偉 I 原詞：林孝謙 <br />\n填詞：DC_  I 演唱：張詩敏<br />\n原曲：有一種悲傷 <br />\n歌名：最後的謊言 <br />\n<br />\n慣了分享夕陽 慣了一起莽撞 <br />\n要說分開自然難猜想 <br />\n<br />\n看你舉止自然 為何特別難過 <br />\n這場故事　將來結局　由我 <br />\n<br />\n別拆穿謊言　扮若無其事消失於你的眼前 <br />\n遵守你意願　最後路程去實現　臨近一天 <br />\n別拆穿謊言　為著能如願可心安滿足　就隨便差遣 <br />\n雖然最後　依然有淚　難免 <br />\n<br />\n和你牽手上路　沒隔膜 <br />\n才算真的快樂 <br />\n<br />\n若到此為止 <br />\n將結果推前　陪你體驗 <br />\n<br />\n別拆穿謊言　為著能如願可心安滿足　就隨便差遣 <br />\n雖然最後　依然有淚　難免 <br />\n別拆穿謊言　但願能留下開心的照片　當記憶碎片 <br />\n交由我們　天堂再會　懷緬"},{"pid":"9785361549534ed20c47f4c4db80ba25e6035626","tid":970004,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78756092ca404fb42dd2e006cf011c8f2fc5c1b0","tid":970004,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a8c4e33e55c9b0644af621fe375ab146ee2ff3","tid":970004,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"要說分開自然難猜想 <br />\n<br />\n唱落好似怪怪地，覺得好橋口<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d967007f4cfb36c0d5d65ec2e16de4d323408448","tid":970004,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"